sentences: Juan Martinez (born 1985), better known by his stage name Down AKA Kilo, is an American rapper from Oxnard, California.
He released his debut album California Cowboyz in 2003, and his second album Definition of an Ese in 2007, with two singles from the album, "Lean like a Cholo" and "Definition of an Ese."
